data.description: Welcome to your dream home located on a quiet cul de sac, close to everything you need! This beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 1/2 bath home boasts hardwood floors on the main level and a cozy wood-burning fireplace in the family room, perfect for relaxing after a long day. The full finished basement offers two outside entrances, a bedroom with an ensuite bath, and plenty of space for entertaining guests. Step outside onto one of the two decks - one on the main level and another off the basement - and enjoy the beautiful views and serene surroundings. Located just minutes away from downtown Gainesville, shopping, walking trails, and Lake Lanier, you'll never run out of things to do! Also, enjoy the convenience of nearby medical facilities. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful home yours - schedule a visit today!
